      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapy doesn't change the reality. the reality is i'm bankrupt and i've disgraced everyone who believed in me. i can't just 'heal' from the fact that i'm a hollow shell of who i was. it feels like every path forward is just a different way of being humiliated every single day. honestly i just want the noise to stop. i just want a way out of this feeling.",
